      <Content>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a title="http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/data/gg702906" href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/data/gg702906"&gt;http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/data/gg702906&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;A 10 minute video on EF Model First&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_2.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_thumb.png" width="584" height="357" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Navigation property allows to go from Blog to the Post, just using properties.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_4.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_thumb_1.png" width="397" height="389" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Right click on design surface and do Generate Database&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_6.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_thumb_2.png" width="381" height="351" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Right click on designer and can do Run SQL.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_8.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_thumb_3.png" width="308" height="260" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Viewing database in Server Explorer in VS.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_10.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_thumb_4.png" width="319" height="307" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Using VS2010 so needed to D/l the DbContext Generator&lt;/p&gt;      &lt;p&gt;Add Code Generation Item on design surface.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_12.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_thumb_5.png" width="331" height="324" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Created an Empty list of CRUD methods, and now creating views.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_14.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Julie-LermanMVC3-and-EF4.1_91B6/image_thumb_6.png" width="270" height="156" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Wire up the Controller to the lightweight DbContext class created by the DbContext generator template (new in 4.1)&lt;/p&gt;</Content>
