      <Content>&lt;p&gt;Quickest way of getting something off the ground using CRUD. &lt;a href="http://channel9.msdn.com/Events/MIX/MIX11/FRM13?format=auto"&gt;http://channel9.msdn.com/Events/MIX/MIX11/FRM13?format=auto&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#160;&amp;#160; EF Code First, Steve Sanderson.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://blog.stevensanderson.com/2011/01/13/scaffold-your-aspnet-mvc-3-project-with-the-mvcscaffolding-package/"&gt;http://blog.stevensanderson.com/2011/01/13/scaffold-your-aspnet-mvc-3-project-with-the-mvcscaffolding-package/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_2.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_thumb.png" width="383" height="398" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Installed MVCScaffolding using NuGet.&amp;#160; Made a Model called Team, then issued the scaffolding command.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_4.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_thumb_1.png" width="244" height="234" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;    &lt;br /&gt;Full CRUD.&amp;#160; No repo pattern.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Changed the model to add another field, make DateTime nullable then how to change the database?&amp;#160; Blow it away!&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_6.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_thumb_2.png" width="312" height="238" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Repo Pattern&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;pre&gt;Scaffold Controller Team –Repository -Force&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Foreign Keys&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://weblogs.asp.net/kiyoshi/archive/2011/06/22/walkthrough-of-entity-framework-4-1-scaffolding-with-mvc-3-0-tools.aspx"&gt;http://weblogs.asp.net/kiyoshi/archive/2011/06/22/walkthrough-of-entity-framework-4-1-scaffolding-with-mvc-3-0-tools.aspx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;





&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_8.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_thumb_3.png" width="244" height="205" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;

  &lt;br /&gt;A product can have a category&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_12.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_thumb_5.png" width="193" height="244" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_14.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/MVC3-Scaffolding_10096/image_thumb_6.png" width="244" height="142" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;







